The police high command has appointed CSP Okuwobi Oluseyi Olabisi as the Public Relations Officer (PRO) to the Nigeria Police Trust Fund (NPTF).
 
Chairman, NPTF Board of Trustees, Suleiman Abba, made the announcement in a statement on Monday. Abba, a retired Inspector General, said Okuwobi would create public awareness about the fund’s mandate and build a sustainable relationship with the public.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .